- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation) is a possible category as the paper deals with the automation of complexity analysis, which is a common topic in symbolic computation. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the automation of a process, which is a common topic in software engineering.
